the input file sig.texi.


@Node Main "sig.guide"



   This document describes @{b}SIRDS_GEN@{ub} V3.7, a shareware @{i}SIRDS@{ui}-Maker for
the Amiga. Many options, random dots as well as patterns are supported.
You can choose between a picture and a mathematical function as source.

Copyright (C) 1994 by Michael Mutschler


 @{" Introduction " Link "Introduction"}              What are SIRDS?
