Installation
************

   To install, you just have to copy (drag) the file to the appropiate
directory.  If you want to have it localized, you have to copy the
appropiate catalog too.  This is easily done by clicking on the
@{b}install_catalog@{ub} icon.


@EndNode

@Node "Registration" "sig.guide/Registration"
@Next "Usage"
@Prev "Installation"
@Toc "Main"

Registration
************

   Starting with V3.1, @{b}SIRDS_GEN@{ub} is now @{i}SHAREWARE@{ui}. There is only a
small cripple, and this is, that the function-parser won't calculate
the following functions:

   @{b}sin, cos, tan, asin, acos, atan, sinh, cosh, tanh, exp, log, log10,
sqrt@{ub}.

   And without registration you wont be able to use pattern mode 4.

   Take a look at the picture @{b}pic2.sirds.gif@{ub}. This one is calculated
with the formula "z=sin(x)+cos(y)" and pattern mode 4.

   The registration fee is US$10, or if you live in germany, you can
send DM15 to me. My address is:

     Michael Mutschler
     Somborer Weg 11
     71067 Sindelfingen
     Germany

   Only US$ or DM are accepted. All I need is your full address with
your name, Street, City and country (just like mine above.)

   You will be shipped a disk with your personal keyfile, and the
newest version of the @{b}SIRDS_GEN@{ub}, with some patterns (and pics, if i get
some via ftp...)

     For all germans: Man kann mir auch die 15DM auch überweisen.
     Meine Konto-Nr ist:

