          Saves the config to a specified file

    @{i}Cancel@{ui}
          Leave the Prefs-Window.

@{b}Edit@{ub}
    @{i}Default@{ui}
          Gets the default values

    @{i}Last saved@{ui}
          reads the config from @{b}ENVARC:SIRDS_GEN.prefs@{ub}

    @{i}Restore@{ui}
          reads the config from @{b}ENV:SIRDS_GEN.prefs@{ub}


