@Node "Version 3.1" "sig.guide/Version 3.1"
@Next "Version 3.2"
@Toc "History"

Version 3.1
===========

   changes for Version 3.1:

   @{b}*@{ub} Bug Fix: when in the Prefs-Win the Source screen-mode was
     disabled, and you disabled the function, the program would crash.

   @{b}*@{ub} Internal changes to the parser.

   @{b}*@{ub} The Parser now translates ^2 ^3 ^4 to multiplications. ^2 is now
     twice as fast.


@EndNode

@Node "Version 3.2" "sig.guide/Version 3.2"
@Next "Version 3.3"
@Prev "Version 3.1"
@Toc "History"

Version 3.2
===========

   changes for Version 3.2:

   @{b}*@{ub} complete rewrite of the options. Now using ReadArgs() instead of
     ArgArrayInit(). See @{"Options" Link "Options"}.

   @{b}*@{ub} Now using ReadPixelArray8() for GIF-saving -> twice as fast as b4.

   @{b}*@{ub} When the pattern can't be loaded, a @{i}SIRDS@{ui} will be drawn.

   @{b}*@{ub} Sometimes, when you clicked the pattern-filerequest Gadget, the
     screen wasn't refreshed. Fixed.

   @{b}*@{ub} Localization. If you want to make a catalog in a language not
     currently supported, please read the readme in the catalogs-dir.

   @{b}*@{ub} Due to localization, I found some strings, which were still
     german. oops.

   @{b}*@{ub} When using @{"[NO]PREFS_FIRST" Link "[NO]PREFS_FIRST"}, and the prefs-window is cancelled, the
     program will quit now.


@EndNode

@Node "Version 3.3" "sig.guide/Version 3.3"
@Next "Version 3.4"
@Prev "Version 3.2"
@Toc "History"

Version 3.3
===========

   changes for Version 3.3:

   @{b}*@{ub} Localized the string "Lines to do" in the Requester when saving a
     gif

   @{b}*@{ub} added new @{"PAT_MODE" Link "PAT_MODE"} 4 for registered users. Without Keyfile you
     wont be able to use it.

   @{b}*@{ub} Enforcer hit removed, when saving the config

   @{b}*@{ub} the dimension of the function will be saved now too

   @{b}*@{ub} serious bug during startup fixed.

   @{b}*@{ub} added cli-option @{"SAVEGIFFILE" Link "SAVEGIFFILE"}.

   @{b}*@{ub} changed DST_WIDTH, DST_HEIGHT, DST_SCREEN to SIRDS_*. But the old
     options will work for a while too... :-)

   @{b}*@{ub} PREFS_FIRST is now true for default

   @{b}*@{ub} added another picture in the archive

   @{b}*@{ub} Now loading locale.library with V38 instead of V39.

   @{b}*@{ub} The error-messages relating the 68020er version of the lack of a
     020 & 881 now localized.


@EndNode

@Node "Version 3.4" "sig.guide/Version 3.4"
@Next "Version 3.5"
@Prev "Version 3.3"
@Toc "History"

Version 3.4
===========

   changes for Version 3.4:

   @{b}*@{ub} removed the flimmering. Didn't look that good, and wasted 1.5kb
     code.  See @{"Introduction" Link "Introduction"}, for a workaround.

   @{b}*@{ub} added "if" function to the function-parser

   @{b}*@{ub} when the source screen wasn't open, the main loop could guru.
     fixed.

   @{b}*@{ub} f & p - key now active again in prefs window.

   @{b}*@{ub} "radius" & "dist" function in parser.

   @{b}*@{ub} Prefs-Win now has the @{i}RMBTRAP@{ui} flag set.


@EndNode

@Node "Version 3.5" "sig.guide/Version 3.5"
@Next "Version 3.6"
@Prev "Version 3.4"
@Toc "History"

Version 3.5
===========

   changes for Version 3.5:

   @{b}*@{ub} removed history of pre 3.1

   @{b}*@{ub} a SIRDS_WIDTH of 640 is now guru-free

   @{b}*@{ub} New option: @{"[NO]PICOSAVE" Link "[NO]PICOSAVE"}

   @{b}*@{ub} french catalog included


@EndNode

@Node "Version 3.6" "sig.guide/Version 3.6"
@Next "Version 3.7"
@Prev "Version 3.5"
@Toc "History"

Version 3.6
===========

   changes for Version 3.6:

   @{b}*@{ub} added @{"MIX" Link "MIX"}-mode

   @{b}*@{ub} fixed pattern mode 1

   @{b}*@{ub} New documentation

   @{b}*@{ub} Made the Preview-Window an AppWindow. You can move patterns
     directly onto it

   @{b}*@{ub} Now the @{b}KEYPATH@{ub} variable is used for searching for the Keyfile. If
     it is not present, @{b}S:@{ub} will be used. Just like @{i}MUI@{ui}.


@EndNode

@Node "Version 3.7" "sig.guide/Version 3.7"
@Next "Version 3.8"
@Prev "Version 3.6"
@Toc "History"

Version 3.7
===========

   V3.6 was only for beta-testing; same as V3.7.

   changes for Version 3.7:

   @{b}*@{ub} added "r" to function-parser (shortcut for rad(x,y))

   @{b}*@{ub} when file loading fails, the program will not quit anymore.
     instead it continues, as if the requester has been cancelled

   @{b}*@{ub} the getpattern filerequester now doesn't automatically disables the
     pattern-mode, when cancelled.

   @{b}*@{ub} added @{i}2.0@{ui}-flag CLI-only option, which forces use of 2.0 function on
     newer OS-versions. This means, no datatypes are used!

   @{b}*@{ub} now the darkest color is used for the BARDETAILPEN and the
     brightest for BARBLOCKPEN. This way you can always see the menu.
     This works on Kick3.0 only.

   @{b}*@{ub} complete rewrite of the internal bitmaps: no more datatypes'
     bitmaps, but my own.  This should solve the big trouble.

   @{b}*@{ub} due to internal bitmaps, you can see the loaded picture under
     Kick2.0 too


@EndNode

@Node "Version 3.8" "sig.guide/Version 3.8"
@Prev "Version 3.7"
@Toc "History"

